{
  "stem": "6966.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I'm going to go underneath the barbed wire, and get into the barrack, and see if they got something to eat there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he went in there and he came back with pockets full of potato peelings.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then it was my turn to do that-- underneath the barbed wire, into the barrack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I saw the most beautiful women, beautiful children, and men-- properly dressed, beautiful gypsy families.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And in the corner I saw a heap of potato peelings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I stuck it in my jacket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I had the big jacket I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And a cap-- big cap full of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then I went out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And bit by bit-- I gave to the boy-- we served potato peelings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Something in-- to get something in their bodies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "The gypsies were gone in a few days' time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We didn't see them anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Finished off.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Anyhow, our time went by.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I stuck it like that seven or eight weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Then comes a big selection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Now they're going to weed out the weak from the strong, from the fit men.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] We're standing in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We had to strip.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There's two tables.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "On each table, there's an SS with a paper in his hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "In the other hand-- a pen or a pencil.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And you've got to walk between the two tables.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And if you don't walk correctly, they direct you to the left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And if you walk all right or you seem all right, they direct you to the right.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "To the left meant the gas chamber, which I did not know at the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "To the right was work elsewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was standing there stripped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm standing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "About a dozen men in front of me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
